org.sakaiproject.tool.assessment.ui.bean.author

Interface CalculatedQuestionAnswerIfc

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CalculatedQuestionFormulaBean, CalculatedQuestionVariableBean

    public interface CalculatedQuestionAnswerIfc
    CalculatedQuestionIfc is an interface that covers the common functionality for variables and formulas that are part of a CalculatedQuestion. Variables and Formulas are both stored in the sam_itemtext_t and sam_answer_t tables and on occasion need to be used similarly.
    Author:
    mgillian
